{"tid":2220284,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"青筋奶女神也脫了！百大網紅性感寫真外流…老司機跪求上車","createTime":"2020-09-27T14:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T15:47:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"009a689395b183112d661b31eb7f6132727b8cc2","tid":2220284,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"「媚娘兒」娛樂公司重金砸下八百萬、籌備八個月，集結台灣百大高人氣女網紅，打造「媚娘兒2020台灣百大網紅聯名寫真」，嚴選收錄了IG人氣美女，除了有百萬粉絲的蕾菈之外，還包括其他高人氣網紅，像是翁子涵、香菱、美麗妄娜、李小星、沈琪琪、邱默默、Jeannine珍琳、Abbie黃艾比、啾啾等美女，寫真集尺度破表，讓粉絲的眼睛大吃冰淇淋。<br />\n<br />\n其中蕾菈透露，很期待這次寫真集的推出，除了努力經營YouTube 創作新內容外，今年還多了一個DJ的新身份，第一場演出就在國際性的S2O舞台，表現相當亮眼，她說當DJ是她的夢想之一，能夠完成這個目標她相當開心，也期待接下來更多舞台機會可與大家見面。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有暗黑版李毓芬的之稱人氣女星香菱分享：「在自己的IG版上有做過測試日系女友感的照片最受歡迎，所以這次特別走粉紅夢幻路線希望可以圈粉成功。」至於因為青筋奶爆紅的啾啾，以及砸下60萬整形成功，讓演藝事業爆發的琪琪，兩位都為了這次的作品穿上比基尼讓粉絲大飽眼福，琪琪表示很開心加入整個寫真集的企劃案，除自己的寫真作品之外，自己很欣賞這次蕾菈照片，覺得她的作品很有態度是男女通吃的好作品。"},{"pid":"09290f1affa80bc28e590114cdfeb6e059c5b5c9","tid":2220284,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/27/2796513-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F2796513-PH.jpg&h=b7bcb156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲翁子涵辣度破表，狂噴鼻血。（圖／媚娘兒提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/27/2796514-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F2796514-PH.jpg&h=9e87a4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲暗黑版李毓芬之稱的香菱，也參與這次寫真集拍攝。（圖／媚娘兒提供）"},{"pid":"a3aa41e15c4605567c5ebda14738992aa18d7a15","tid":2220284,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/27/2796524-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F2796524-PH.jpg&h=e9197625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蕾菈披上浪漫婚紗拍攝寫真。（圖／媚娘兒提）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/27/2796517-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F2796517-PH.jpg&h=0765c2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲因青筋奶爆紅的啾啾，這次換上比基尼讓粉絲大飽眼福。（圖／媚娘兒提供）"},{"pid":"d803c08faf928aa49917f3bd5539b11c0ede94a0","tid":2220284,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/27/2796512-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F2796512-PH.jpg&h=76326e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲沈琪琪。（圖／媚娘兒提供）"},{"pid":"f3ca9e2ceea0a6e94b419989ab7e3fc5bc070ca8","tid":2220284,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"no<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c971d966b73399ee48a7ed613b775147cc3627ab","tid":2220284,"uid":33077,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:04:44.000Z","msg":"嘩咩黎架 毫無美感"},{"pid":"8fb4cb66bec257d7cb1a751022b6ce7569408ec3","tid":2220284,"uid":261849,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:05:00.000Z","msg":"啲樣真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf21210e0b0c92023738377897b08d5fca3bba3","tid":2220284,"uid":378357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"施丹你係咪接咗part time PR<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點解一晚可以出咁多post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59831a32b5c7357401711ba6a7cee38f1e72418a","tid":2220284,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4bf21210e0b0c92023738377897b08d5fca3bba3","tid":22